You can become a Beta Tester by subscribing to the Farm RPG [Patreon] and paying $10 a month.

After you subscribe, [b]SEND A MESSAGE ON PATREON[/b] with your in-game username so Firestream can get your benefits started!

Beta testing takes place here on the live game when features are added.  The new additions will be usable by Beta Testers only for a certain amount of time before becoming available to everybody else.  Feedback from testing is also encouraged!  Keep an eye on [patreon] and [updates] to know what to look for.

You get 200 Gold instantly when you subscribe and 200 Gold on the 1st of every month as long as you are still subscribed

